V0218_01_00_00_0.text: This era must end for a new one to rise.

V0218_01_00_01_0.text: I have chosen the path of destruction - one you must accept.

V0218_01_00_02_0.text: If you choose to fight me, your existence is over.

V0218_01_00_03_0.text: I will annihilate this world to create a bright future.

V0218_01_00_04_0.text:
Aporia, you know how strong I am.
You know you cannot win.

V0218_01_00_05_0.text: Aporia, need I remind you that hope is an illusion?

V0218_01_00_06_0.text:
Antinomy, you're a dreamer.
And dreams aren't real.

V0218_01_00_07_0.text: Paradox, show me the results of your research.

V0218_01_00_08_0.text: Yusei, everything you believe in is pointless against me.

V0218_03_00_00_0.text: If you keep fighting, I will do what needs to be done.

V0218_03_00_01_0.text: The longer you continue, the more you'll suffer.

V0218_03_00_03_0.text: There is no hope for this world.

V0218_03_00_04_0.text: So that's the strategy you want to use against me.

V0218_03_00_05_0.text: The sliver of a chance you think you have isn't real.

V0218_05_00_00_0.text: No matter what you attempt, you can't save the world!

V0218_06_01_03_0.text: This will erase all illusions you have of winning.

V0218_07_09_00_0.text: I flip over my Set card.

V0218_07_09_01_0.text: This is the card I Set.

V0218_11_01_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Defense Position.

V0218_14_00_01_0.text: With this battle, you will kneel before your superior.

V0218_15_00_02_0.text: You do not even have an ounce of hope.

V0218_16_00_00_0.text: Whatever hope you had is gone.

V0218_16_00_01_0.text: You're not good enough to save this world.

V0218_21_00_00_0.text: You can't defeat me if you only defend.

V0218_21_00_01_0.text:
What can you do?
You have very few LP left.

V0218_21_00_04_0.text: I know you think you have a chance, but you don't.

V0218_21_00_05_0.text: If you believe you can change the future, defeat me.

V0218_28_00_00_0.text:
The Timelords rule all.
They are impossible to defeat.

V0218_28_00_01_0.text: You now know as I do that there is no such thing as hope.

V0218_28_00_02_0.text:
You learned a harsh truth today.
That miracles don't exist.

V0218_28_00_03_0.text: Summoning Synchro Monsters is useless against my Timelords.

V0218_28_00_04_0.text:
There is no hope in the future.
Only despair.

V0218_28_00_04_1.text: You know that better than anyone, Aporia.

V0218_28_00_05_0.text: Antinomy, you held on tightly to a tiny sliver of hope.

V0218_28_00_05_1.text: But reality proved it never existed.

V0218_28_00_06_0.text:
Paradox, you can't change the future.
Your mission failed.

V0218_28_00_07_0.text: Yusei Fudo, I am you in the future.

V0218_28_00_07_1.text: That is why I know your every strategy.

V0218_28_00_08_0.text: Saving one person requires the sacrifice of another.

V0218_28_00_08_1.text: You are naive if you think you can save everyone.

V0218_29_00_00_0.text:
No...
This isn't how it happened in the history books...

V0218_29_00_01_0.text:
Aporia...
Antinomy...
Paradox...
I'll be joining you soon...

V0218_29_00_03_0.text: Was everything I've done a mistake...

V0218_29_00_04_0.text: Aporia, so this is the hope that you found...

V0218_29_00_05_0.text: I see why your new friends have instilled you with hope.

V0218_29_00_06_0.text:
Well done, Paradox.
But it's not enough to save the future.

V0218_29_00_07_0.text: I wish I could see the new future you are creating...

V0218_29_00_08_0.text:
Yusei, only you can lead humanity.
I know you can do it.

V0218_33_00_01_0.text: Everything you believe in - I shall destroy.

V0218_33_00_02_0.text: Let your eyes see the infinite power of the Timelords.

V0218_30_00_00_0.text: You are living up to your potential.

V0218_30_00_01_0.text: All futures are still possible - which one will you seize?

V0218_30_00_02_0.text: You must believe in the path you chose.

V0218_34_00_00_0.text: I did this on purpose to give you false hope.

V0218_34_00_01_0.text: The Timelords are ultimate beings born from the infinite.

V0218_34_00_02_0.text:
What's wrong?
Didn't you say a miracle was always possible?

V0218_34_00_03_0.text:
Heh heh.
Perhaps you never intended to attack?

V0218_34_00_04_0.text:
Heh heh.
You made the correct move.

V0218_34_00_05_0.text: Do you think you can stall forever?

V0218_34_00_06_0.text: Tales of your heroism still exist in my era.

V0218_34_00_07_0.text: To save the world, I must become Yusei Fudo.

V0218_34_00_08_0.text: I have very little time left.

V0218_34_00_09_0.text: I already have a counterstrategy for that.

V0218_34_00_10_0.text: I have the right to change history.

V0218_35_00_00_0.text: I am Z-one, the last survivor on Earth.

V0218_35_00_01_0.text: A new future will soon begin.

V0218_36_00_04_0.text: Aporia, help me change the future.

V0218_36_00_05_0.text: I leave this to you, Antinomy.

V0218_08_00_00_0.text: I activate my Continuous Trap, Empty Machine.

V0218_08_00_02_0.text: I'll get rid of Empty Machine to activate Infinite Machine.

V0218_08_00_03_1.text: Bear witness to Timelord's infinite power.

V0218_08_00_04_0.text: I send Infinite Machine to the Grave to play Infinite Light.

V0218_08_00_04_1.text: My Timelords will never leave my side again.

V0218_08_00_05_1.text: I can call forth Timelords from my hand, deck and Graveyard.

V0218_08_00_06_0.text: I activate my Trap, Foolish Decision.

V0218_08_00_07_0.text: I activate the Trap, Magician's Adage.

V0218_08_00_08_0.text:
I activate my Trap.
Empress's Staff.

V0218_08_00_09_0.text:
I activate my Trap.
Empress's Crown.

V0218_08_00_10_0.text: Z-ONE's effect activates when it's destroyed.

V0218_08_00_10_1.text: I get a Continuous Spell or Field Spell from my Graveyard.

V0218_08_00_11_0.text: I activate my Spell Card, Mooyan Curry.

V0218_08_00_12_0.text: I activate my Spell Card, Dian Keto the Cure Master.

V0218_09_00_00_1.text: I Special Summon a Fairy monster from my hand or Graveyard.

V0218_09_00_00_2.text: This monster's effects are negated, but its ATK become 4000.

V0218_09_00_01_0.text: Learn just how powerless you are.

V0218_09_00_01_1.text: I activate Sephylon, the Ultimate Timelord's effect.

V0218_09_00_02_0.text: When Gabrion, the Timelord battles, its effect activates.

V0218_09_00_02_1.text: All cards on your field return to the deck.

V0218_09_00_02_2.text: Then you draw the same number of cards you returned.

V0218_09_00_03_1.text: This card returns to the deck.

V0218_09_00_04_0.text: Since Kamion battled, its effect activates.

V0218_09_00_04_1.text: One of your cards returns to the deck, and you take damage.

V0218_09_00_05_1.text: This card returns to the deck.

V0218_09_00_06_0.text: Since Sadion battled, its effect activates.

V0218_09_00_07_1.text: This card returns to the deck.

V0218_09_00_08_0.text: Since Zaphion battled, its effect activates.

V0218_09_00_08_1.text: All Spell and Trap cards on your field return to the deck.

V0218_09_00_09_0.text: Zaphion activates when it goes from the field to the Grave.

V0218_09_00_10_1.text: This card returns to the deck.

V0218_09_00_11_0.text: Since Sandaion battled, its effect activates.

V0218_09_00_12_1.text: This card returns to the deck.

V0218_09_00_13_0.text: Since Hailon battled, its effect activates.

V0218_09_00_14_1.text: This card returns to the deck.

V0218_09_00_15_1.text: If this card battled, your LP are halved.

V0218_09_00_16_1.text: This card returns to the deck.

V0218_09_00_17_0.text: Metaion, the Timelord activates its effect if it battled.

V0218_09_00_17_1.text: All other monsters return to the hand, and you take damage.

V0218_09_00_18_1.text: This card returns to the deck.

V0218_09_00_19_0.text: Since Lazion battled, its effect activates.

V0218_09_00_19_1.text: All cards in your Graveyard return to your deck.

V0218_09_00_20_1.text: When you draw, you take damage.

V0218_09_00_21_1.text: This card returns to the deck.

V0218_09_00_22_0.text: Since Raphion battled, take its effect.

V0218_09_00_23_1.text: This card returns to the deck.

V0218_09_00_24_0.text: Timelord Progenitor Vorpgate activates its effect.

V0218_09_00_24_1.text: After it battles, all monsters on your field are banished.

V0218_09_00_25_1.text: All monsters it banished are Special Summoned to your field.

V0218_09_00_26_0.text: I Tribute Time Maiden to activate her effect.

V0218_09_00_26_1.text: I add a Timelord in my deck with 0 ATK to my hand.

V0218_09_00_27_0.text: I banish Time Maiden from my Graveyard to use her effect.

V0218_09_00_27_1.text: She Special Summons a Timelord with 0 ATK from my deck.

V0218_37_00_00_0.text: Beyond the light of the Timelords lies the true secret.

V0218_37_00_00_1.text: Where emptiness transforms into the infinite!

V0218_13_00_01_0.text:
Witness my true power!
The essence of all!

V0218_37_00_01_0.text: The hopes of the world open the door to a new  era!

V0218_37_00_02_0.text: The hopes of the world coalesce into a single star.

V0218_37_00_02_1.text:
Let's rev it up.
Synchro Summon!

V0218_37_00_04_0.text: Spread your wings and soar to new heights.

V0218_37_00_04_1.text:
Be transformed by the winds of destiny.
Accel Synchro!

V0218_37_00_05_0.text: It's time to rev it up!

V0218_37_00_06_0.text:
Form the road of light!
Delta Accel Synchro!

V0218_26_00_02_0.text: Those simple tricks don't work against me.
